<button class="intent" data-route="control"><span class="tag">03 / ENGINEERING</span><b>先看工程</b><span>直接检查 ST、75/0 证据级别和三页 HMI 分工。</span></button>
<button class="intent" data-route="materials"><span class="tag">06 / REPRODUCE</span><b>直接查证</b><span>从结论跳到命令、文件与复现入口，而非重复翻卡片。</span></button>
</div>
