</section>
<section class="chapter" role="tabpanel" id="panel-method" aria-labelledby="tab-method" hidden>
<div class="eyebrow">MODEL → CONSTRAINT → POLICY</div><h2>先保证可行，再比较策略。</h2><p class="lede">算法的价值不来自“智能”标签，而来自统一到达流、统一运动学、明确约束门和可重放随机种子下的公平比较。</p>
<div class="method-grid"><div class="method-flow">
<div class="method-step"><i>01</i><div><b>货物画像</b><small>重量、体积、频次、类别与到达情景</small></div></div>
<div class="method-step"><i>02</i><div><b>可行性守卫</b><small>占用、承重、体积与边界先行</small></div></div>
<div class="method-step"><i>03</i><div><b>运动学代价</b><small>双轴同动；报告主口径使用梯形加减速（sim）</small></div></div>
<div class="method-step"><i>04</i><div><b>策略库选择</b><small>AWRA-LS、CB、TOB 与基线统一比较</small></div></div>
<div class="method-step"><i>05</i><div><b>泛化验证</b><small>固定最终测试入口；30-seed untouched</small></div></div>
</div><aside class="fact-sheet"><h3>模型事实卡</h3><dl>
<div><dt>几何</dt><dd>20 列×20 层；单巷道、单堆垛机</dd></div><div><dt>时间</dt><dd>双轴同动的切比雪夫完成时间</dd></div>
<div><dt>速度</dt><dd>VX=2.0 m/s；VZ=0.5 m/s（sim 设计口径）</dd></div><div><dt>加速度</dt><dd>AX=0.5；AZ=0.3 m/s²（sim）</dd></div>
<div><dt>驻留</dt><dd>取货与放货各 4.0 s（sim）</dd></div></dl></aside></div>
</section>
<section class="chapter" role="tabpanel" id="panel-control" aria-labelledby="tab-control" hidden>
